original_title: UFC Fight Night 66: Edgar vs. Faber
overview: UFC Fight Night 66: Edgar vs. Faber was a mixed martial arts event held on May 16, 2015, at the Mall of Asia Arena in Pasay, Philippines. The event was headlined by a featherweight bout between former UFC Lightweight champion Frankie Edgar and former WEC Featherweight champion Urijah Faber.
title: UFC Fight Night 66: Edgar vs. Faber
